snippet.title: Alpine Lake - Official Announcement - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Demo and Wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2341620/Alpine_Lake/

Alpine Lake is a cozy Life-Sim, Innkeeper-Sim. Inspired by Stardew Valley, The Sims, and Animal Crossing, Alpine Lake lets you unleash your creativity and design any kind of inn, bed and breakfast, or hotel you can imagine! Construct the walls, the floors, and furniture to design the perfect haven for your guests.

A solo project by  @booyagrandmma 
I like to frequent many social channels! Feel free to follow along on your favorite.
https://www.mossygrovegames.com/games
https://www.tiktok.com/@mossygrovegames
https://www.instagram.com/alpinelakegame
https://www.twitch.tv/booyagrandmma
https://discord.gg/Vx4tfWC5Xj

Music by Eric Hamilton - http://www.erichamilton.net
